Class Cell

java.lang.Object
zombicide.grid.cell.Cell
Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Cell extends Object
This class is an abstract representation of a cell.

      public List<Cell> inRange1(Cell[][] grid)
      Returns a list of neighboring cells that are within a range of 1 cell. The neighboring cells include the current cell itself.
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      a list of neighboring cells within a range of 1 cell

    • inRange3

      public List<Cell> inRange3(Cell[][] grid)
      Returns a list of cells that are within a range of 3 cells from the current cell. The range is determined by the number of rows and columns in the grid.
      Parameters:
      grid - the 2D array of cells representing the game grid
      Returns:
      a list of cells within the range of 3 cells from the current cell
